niethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"aee9b6515c361ed59a894d00442856e35b715b9d","tid":1640390,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"停止使用火魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77518f1ade4416b4c6f7682e15fb6cd233f97969","tid":1640390,"uid":15337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"5毛post, 亂鳩UP.<br />\n人地指火魔法唔夠完美啊~"},{"pid":"12448ddb7f2acb3c602bae2d7805bdefe858833d","tid":1640390,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77518f1ade4416b4c6f7682e15fb6cd233f97969","tid":1640390,"uid":15337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"5毛post, 亂鳩UP.<br />\n人地指火魔法唔夠完美啊~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"你唔識英文?"},{"pid":"9fae18fe0de7921efb06c849c6f63cc81f76b1e9","tid":1640390,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7d82a0cea971e742e0d1869a5a9b8a2dbc236b","tid":1640390,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12448ddb7f2acb3c602bae2d7805bdefe858833d","tid":1640390,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77518f1ade4416b4c6f7682e15fb6cd233f97969","tid":1640390,"uid":15337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:04:38.